data.description: Location! Location! Location! This charming home is located in one of OKC's most established neighborhoods. Do you envision driving home to established tree lined streets...then this home is for you. This adorable bungalow sits stately on its lot. It has three bedrooms, two bathrooms and a two car garage. The living room and dining/kitchen area are both extremely oversized and has a perfect flow for entertaining or a cozy evening at home. It features a wonderful vaulted living room, stunning fireplace and access to the fully fenced backyard. The primary bedroom has an ensuite bath. The two secondary bedrooms are spacious. This home has been well loved.  Spacious and peaceful backyard will be your own private oasis. Perfect for relaxing or outdoor entertaining. Conveniently located to shopping, restaurants, highways and medical. This is your opportunity to be in the heart of the city.
